Author: Frederic Bertrand [cre, aut] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0837-8281>), Myriam Maumy [aut] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4615-1512>)
Maintainer: Frederic Bertrand <frederic.bertrand@lecnam.net>
Description: Provides partial least squares regression and various regular or 
  sparse techniques for fitting models to big data. Provides a Partial Least 
  Squares (PLS) regression algorithm that works with bigmemory matrices without 
  loading the entire dataset in memory. Also implements a gradient-descent based 
  solver that works directly on 'bigmemory' matrices.
